<h2>New Ticket Submitted</h2>

<p>A new support ticket has been submitted by <strong><%= @ticket.customer.name %></strong> (<%= @ticket.customer.email %>) :</p>

<table style="border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><strong>Title:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><%= @ticket.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><strong>Description:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><%= @ticket.description %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><strong>Status:</strong></td>
    <td style="padding: 6px;"><%= @ticket.status.humanize %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>Please log in to the admin dashboard to review and assign this ticket.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>Support System</p>
